ubx_message.comment: This message reports the precise BDS time of the most recent navigation solution including validity flags and an accuracy estimate.

payload_fields.name: iTOW
payload_fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See section iTOW timestamps in the integration manual for details.

payload_fields.name: SOW
payload_fields.description: BDS time of week (rounded to seconds)

payload_fields.name: fSOW
payload_fields.description: Fractional part of SOW (range: +/-500000000). The precise BDS time of week in seconds is: SOW + fSOW * 1e-9

payload_fields.name: week
payload_fields.description: BDS week number of the navigation epoch

payload_fields.name: leaps
payload_fields.description: BDS leap seconds (BDS-UTC)

payload_fields.name: valid
payload_fields.description: Validity Flags

bit_fields.name: sowValid
bit_fields.description: 1 = Valid SOW and fSOW (see section Time validity in the integration manual for details)

bit_fields.name: weekValid
bit_fields.description: 1 = Valid week (see section Time validity in the integration manual for details)

payload_fields.name: tAcc
payload_fields.description: Time Accuracy Estimate
